text: Maybe Better is an Australian Thoroughbred racehorse who won the 2006 Group 3 Saab Quality2006 Saab Quality result and finished 3rd in the 2006 Melbourne Cup when ridden by Chris Munce.2006 Melbourne Cup result Maybe Better started in 29 races for 6 wins, 3 2nds and 2 3rds, with earnings of A$959,600. ==References== ;Notes ;Sources * Maybe Better's racing record Category:Racehorses bred in Australia
title: Maybe Better
